### 🔴 422. Gold Loan Company

**What it is:** Lending money against gold jewelry as collateral — quick disbursement (30 minutes), lower risk due to collateral.

**Players:** Muthoot Finance (big — ₹60,000Cr+ AUM), Manappuram (big), IIFL Gold (big), individual gold loan companies.

