**Challenges:** 📜 NBFC license + gold storage regulations · 💰 Capital for lending + vault infrastructure · ⚙ Gold authentication (fake gold risk) · 📜 Auction process for unpaid loans.

**Mistake:** Not having proper gold testing equipment. One fake gold loan = total loss. XRF (X-ray fluorescence) testing is mandatory for every item pledged.

**One-liner:** Lend against gold — XRF testing on every item is mandatory; one fake piece = total loss on that loan.

