### 🟡 426. Business Loan Platform

**What it is:** Digital platform for small business loans — quick approval using alternative data (GST returns, bank statements, POS data).

**Players:** Lendingkart (Indian, big), NeoGrowth (Indian, medium), FlexiLoans (Indian, medium), Indifi (Indian).

**Model:** Product Sale 📦 (interest income) + Commission 💰 (if marketplace model) | **Revenue:** 🔄 Medium.

