### 🔴 427. Buy-Now-Pay-Later (BNPL)

**What it is:** Offering instant credit at point of purchase — online and offline. Customer pays later in installments, usually interest-free for short periods.

**Players:** Simpl (Indian, medium), LazyPay (big), ZestMoney (Indian, shuttered), Bajaj Finserv (big).

**Model:** Commission 💰 (merchant discount rate) + Product Sale 📦 (interest on longer terms) | **Revenue:** 🔄 Medium.

