**Mistake:** Buying trucks on loan without guaranteed load. EMI is fixed; loads aren't. Contract with shippers for guaranteed loads BEFORE buying trucks.

**One-liner:** Run truck fleet — secure guaranteed load contracts before EMI commitments; idle trucks bleed cash.

