**Model:** Service Fee 🔧 (per-shipment) | **Revenue:** ⚡ Fast.

**Challenges:** 📈 E-commerce giants building own logistics · ⚙ Last-mile delivery complexity · 💰 Thin per-shipment margins · ⚙ Lost/damaged packages hurt reputation.

**Mistake:** Trying to build a national network from scratch. Start hyperlocal (one city), dominate last-mile, then partner for intercity through hub-and-spoke.

**One-liner:** Run courier services — start hyperlocal and dominate one city before going intercity.

