**Challenges:** 📈 Digital platforms disintermediating traditional brokers · 💰 Shippers delay payments · ⚙ Driver/truck reliability.

**Mistake:** Not adding technology. Traditional phone-based brokers are losing. Even basic WhatsApp-based tracking puts you ahead.

**One-liner:** Match goods with trucks — add technology (even basic tracking) to survive digital disruption.

