**Players:** Zoomcar (Indian, self-drive), Myles (Indian), Orix (leasing, big), ALD Automotive (leasing, big).

**Model:** Rental 🔑 | **Revenue:** 🔄 Medium.

**Challenges:** 💰 Fleet investment ₹5L-5Cr+ · ⚙ Vehicle maintenance + insurance · 📈 Zoomcar/Revv (now Uber) dominating self-drive · 📜 Commercial permits for leasing.

**Mistake:** Only offering self-drive to tourists. Corporate leasing (3-5 year employee car leases) is higher margin and more predictable than daily rentals.

**One-liner:** Rent cars — corporate leasing offers predictable, higher-margin revenue vs volatile daily rentals.

