### 🟡 462. Bike & Scooter Rental

**What it is:** Renting two-wheelers — tourist destinations, daily commute, micro-mobility.

**Players:** Bounce (Indian, big), Vogo (Indian), Yulu (electric, Indian), individual rental operators in tourist spots.

**Model:** Rental 🔑 | **Revenue:** ⚡ Fast.

**Challenges:** ⚙ Vehicle maintenance (renters abuse vehicles) · 💰 Theft risk · 📜 Insurance and permits · 📈 E-scooter sharing growing.

**Mistake:** Not having GPS tracking on every vehicle. Theft and unauthorized usage are the #1 risk. GPS + kill switch on every vehicle.

**One-liner:** Rent two-wheelers — GPS tracking and kill switch on every vehicle; theft is the biggest risk.

