### 🔴 463. Ambulance Fleet

**What it is:** Operating a fleet of ambulances — emergency (108 model), non-emergency patient transport, event medical services.

**Players:** GVK EMRI 108 (big, PPP), Stanplus (Indian), Medulance (Indian, small).

**Model:** Service Fee 🔧 + Contract 📋 (government/hospital) | **Revenue:** 🔄 Medium.

**Challenges:** 💰 Equipped ambulance ₹15L-50L each · ⚙ 24/7 readiness · 🧠 Paramedic staffing · 📜 State ambulance regulations · 💰 Government payments are slow.

**Mistake:** Buying vehicles without medical equipment. An ambulance without defibrillator, oxygen, and stretcher is a van, not an ambulance.

**One-liner:** Run ambulance fleet — medical equipment and paramedic training are non-negotiable.

