### 🟡 464. School Bus Service

**What it is:** Operating school bus fleet — contracted by schools for student pick-up and drop-off.

**Players:** Individual school bus operators, Shuttl (Indian — corporate/school shuttles), schools with own buses.

**Model:** Contract 📋 (annual school contract) + Service Fee 🔧 | **Revenue:** 🔄 Medium.

**Challenges:** 📜 Strict safety requirements (speed governors, cameras, female attendant mandate) · ⚙ Route optimization for 100+ students · 🌊 School holidays = zero revenue for months · 💰 Bus cost ₹15L-40L.

**Mistake:** Not investing in GPS tracking and parent notification. Modern parents demand real-time bus tracking via app. Schools choose operators who provide this technology.

**One-liner:** Run school buses — GPS tracking with parent app is now expected by schools; operators without technology lose contracts.

