### 🟡 465. Airport Shuttle Service

**What it is:** Operating shuttle buses between airports and city centers, hotels, IT parks, convention centers.

**Players:** BMTC (Bengaluru), individual airport shuttle operators, hotel-operated shuttles.

**Model:** Service Fee 🔧 (per-passenger or contract) | **Revenue:** 🔄 Medium.

**Challenges:** 📜 Airport authority permits · 📈 Ola/Uber competing for airport rides · ⚙ Flight delay management (schedule disruptions) · 💰 Airport access fees.

**Mistake:** Running fixed schedules only. Demand-responsive shuttles (departing when full or on-demand) maximize utilization vs empty fixed-schedule runs.

**One-liner:** Run airport shuttles — demand-responsive scheduling beats fixed schedules for utilization.

