### 🔴 467. Charter & Helicopter Service

**What it is:** Operating chartered aircraft or helicopters — VIP transport, medical evacuation, tourism, corporate travel, aerial survey.

**Players:** Pawan Hans (PSU, big), Global Vectra (Indian), individual charter operators.

**Model:** Rental 🔑 (per-hour flight charge) | **Revenue:** 🔄 Medium.

**Challenges:** 💰 Helicopter ₹5Cr-50Cr+ · 📜 DGCA Air Operator Permit — extremely stringent · 🧠 Qualified pilots + engineering · ⚙ Maintenance costs astronomical · 📈 Limited demand in India.

**Mistake:** Buying aircraft before securing clients. Lease don't buy initially. Idle aircraft cost ₹50K-5L per day in parking, insurance, and depreciation.

**One-liner:** Operate charter flights — lease before buying; idle aircraft costs ₹50K-5L per day.

