### 🟡 474. Packaging & Palletization

**What it is:** Designing and providing packaging solutions for logistics — export packaging, pallet loading optimization, protective packaging, container stuffing.

**Players:** Individual packaging service providers, LEAP India (Indian), Signode (big, global).

**Model:** Service Fee 🔧 + Product Sale 📦 | **Revenue:** 🔄 Medium.

**Challenges:** ⚙ Every product has different packaging needs · 📈 Commodity packaging has thin margins · 🧠 Must understand shipping stresses (vibration, humidity, stacking).

**Mistake:** Only selling standard boxes. Custom protective packaging (foam inserts, VCI paper for metals, desiccants) has 3-5x margins over commodity corrugated.

**One-liner:** Provide logistics packaging — custom protective solutions have 3-5x margins over standard boxes.

